Package: pkgreviewr
Type: Package
Title: Review R Packages with Deterministic QA Signals and LLM Summaries
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Who wrote it
Maintainer: The package maintainer <yourself@somewhere.net>
Description: Collects deterministic review signals for R packages, including
    check, lint, coverage, and extracted source context, then uses an LLM to
    generate section-based review reports with concise section summaries and a
    synthesized overall diagnostic.
